-- Cosatu Calls for Pick n Pay Boycott Until Pay Dispute With Union Settled
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-10-29T08:58:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/cosatu-calls-for-pick-n-pay-boycott-until-pay-dispute-with-union-settled.html
The Congress of South African Trade
Unions, the country’s largest labor federation, called on its
members to boycott Pick n Pay Stores Ltd. until a pay and
benefits dispute with the SA Commercial, Catering and Allied
Workers’ Union is resolved.  The labor federation commented in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  